    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "on their own terms... i guess. but it feels like i'm just fighting something that doesn't want to let go. if the most honest thing is to just let the code stop, then why does it feel so wrong to say it would be better if they just weren't here at all? like, wouldn't it be better for everyone if the erasure just happened now?",
